ase and proficiency in the laws of the relevant jurisdiction.</p><p>THE CONTENTS OF THIS SITE, INCLUDING, WITHOUT LIMITATION, THE MATERIALS, ARE PROVIDED &#8220;AS IS,&#8221; AND SPREADIT MAKES NO REPRESENTATIONS OR WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, WITH RESPECT TO THIS SITE OR ITS CONTENTS. SPREADIT DISCLAIMS ALL REPRESENTATIONS AND WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, INCLUDING, WITHOUT LIMITATION, WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY, FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, TITLE AND NONINFRINGEMENT.</p><h2>LIMITATION OF LIABILITY</h2><p>Neither SPREADIT nor any of its officers, members, directors, employees or other representatives will be liable for any damages, special, consequential or otherwise, arising out of or in connection with the use of this Site or any information contained herein even if advised of the possibility thereof. This limitation of liability is comprehensive and applies to all damages of any kind, including, without limitation, loss of data, income or profit, loss of or damage to property, claims of third parties and civil/criminal prosecution.</p><p>You have sole responsibility for adequate protection and backup of data and/or equipment used in connection with the Site and will not make any claim against SPREADIT for lost data, re-run time, inaccurate output, work delays or lost profits resulting from the use of the materials.</p><p>As a visitor to and a user of this Site, you, in effect, agree that all access and use of this Site and its contents are at your own risk.</p><h2>SUBMISSIONS</h2><p>While we welcome comments and feedback regarding this Site, SPREADIT is under no obligation to respond to all pieces of correspondence received through this Site, to maintain submitted comments in confidence, or to pay compensation of any kind for your comments or submissions. We do not wish to receive any confidential or proprietary ideas, suggestions, materials, or information via this Site or any email connection. All unsolicited comments, feedback, ideas, suggestions, and other submissions that are disclosed or submitted to SPREADIT through this Site shall become and remain the property of SPREADIT. Any such submission by you is a declaration of the full release of all proprietary claims and/or intellectual rights regarding your submission.</p><h2>LINKS TO THIRD PARTY SITES</h2><p>Any other websites that are accessible via links on this Site are not under the control of SPREADIT. SPREADIT is not responsible for the content of any linked site or any link contained in a linked site, or any changes or updates to the information contained in such sites. SPREADIT provides the linked sites to you only as a convenience and the inclusion of any such link on the Site does not imply SPREADIT&#8217;s endorsement of the site, the organization operating such site, or any products or services of that organization. Your linking to any off-site pages or other sites is entirely at your own risk. Under no circumstances will SPREADIT be held responsible or liable, directly or indirectly, for any loss or damage that is caused or alleged to have been caused to you in connection with your use of, or reliance on, any content, goods or services available on any other site.</p><h2>LINKS TO WWW.SPREADITGLOBAL.COM</h2><p>SPREADIT permits third party sites to link to SPREADIT&#8217;s Site located at www.SpreadIt.ng pursuant to these terms and conditions:</p><p>Links may be text-based using the words: &#8220;International Trademark Association,&#8221; &#8220;SPREADIT&#8221; or &#8220;SpreadIt.ng&#8221;. You may not use the SPREADIT logo or any other trademark as a link to SPREADIT.</p><p>By linking, you acknowledge and agree that, other than as set forth herein, all rights to SPREADIT marks, the content appearing on the SPREADIT website and the design of the SPREADIT website belong to SPREADIT.</p><p>You may not create frames around SPREADIT’s webpages or use other techniques that alter in any way the visual presentation or appearance of the Site.</p><p>You must not misrepresent your relationship with SPREADIT or present false or misleading impressions about SPREADIT. No links to the Site may be used in a manner that implies or suggests that SPREADIT approves or endorses you, your website or your goods and services (in all cases, except as SPREADIT may have agreed separately with you in writing).</p><p>SPREADIT shall have no responsibility or liability for any content appearing on your website. You agree to indemnify and defend SPREADIT against all claims arising out of or based upon your website.</p><p>No link(s) may appear on any page on your website or within any context containing content or materials that may be interpreted as libelous, obscene or criminal, or which infringes, otherwise violates, or advocates the infringement or other violation of, any third party rights.</p><p>SPREADIT reserves the right at any time and in its sole discretion to request that you remove all links or any particular link to the Site from your website.</p><h2>REFERENCES TO PRODUCTS OR SERVICES</h2><p>Information on this Site may contain references or cross references to SPREADIT products or services that are not announced or available in your country. Such references do not imply that SPREADIT intends to announce such products or services in your country. Please contact SPREADIT for information regarding the products and services that may be available to you.</p><h2>GOVERNING LAW</h2><p>These terms and conditions will be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the Federal Republic of Nigeria, without regard to any principles of conflicts of law. You agree that any action at law or in equity that arises out of or relates to these terms and conditions will be filed only in the state or federal courts located in Nigeria.</p><h2>COMPLETE AGREEMENT</h2><p>These terms and conditions, and policies referred to in these terms and conditions, represent the entire understanding relating to the use of the Site and prevail over any prior or contemporaneous, conflicting or additional, communications. SPREADIT reserves the right to revise these terms and conditions at any time without notice by updating this posting.</p><h2>INQUIRIES</h2><p>Thank you for visiting SpreadIt.ng. For questions concerning policies, contact info@spreaditglobal.com</p><p><!--CONTENT ENDS--></p><p><!--CONTENT START--></p><h2>YOU UNDERSTAND THAT BY USING THIS SITE</h2><p>You are required to agree to the below terms and conditions of usage. Please note the following:</p><p>You must complete a detailed Registration Form that may request personal information for our data base.<br />You are required to provide the following information for our database:</p><p><i>First Name</i></p><p>Last Name</p><p>Email Address</p><p>Phone number</p><p>Password</p><p><b>Bank Account Details</b> &#8211; <i>Account Name, Account Number, Bank</i> (We need this so we can refund you in the event that you cancel your order).</p><p>You understand that the information you have provided is assumed to be correct and we will not be held liable for any damages arising from any wrong information provided.</p><p>SpreadIt shall not be held liable for any claims or loss arising from the information you provide for any transaction. Consequently, you hereby agree to indemnify SpreadIt against all and any liability, loss, claims, costs and charges arising from all and any information you provide, including legal costs.<br />Note that due to Bank charges and charges by our payment processor, which today is Paystack, we deduct between 5.5% and 7.5% of the refundable amount in a case of refund OR an N100 inconvenience fee. We will charge the higher of the two amounts. Kindly note that this can change anytime without any notice.</p><p>After you have Signed Up, you may be required to upload a profile image. You are also encouraged to first read up our FAQ&#8217;s to guide you through your transactions on Spreadit.ng. Follow the ink to view our FAQ&#8217;s. Our FAQs deal with all matters partaining to how we operate in Spreadit. By signing up and using our services you consent that you fully understand and agree with the answers we have provided.</p><p>From order to delivery takes between 10 &#8211; 20 working days except for peak periods like Christmas and Chinese New Year.</p><p><!--CONTENT ENDS--></p>					</div>
